creator: Tribal Group
descriptionHtml:
Highlands Connect puts all the information you need to know about College life in one place - on your phone.

With your own easy-to-use, personalised dashboard, you will have 24/7 access to all the stuff that matters to you.

Alerts will mean that you never miss an important piece of information again: whether it be around unexpected College closures; timetable changes or deadline reminders.

Some of the key features include:
- Timetable – full access to your timetable, with notifications if anything changes
- Map – find your way around the campus
- Daily updates from Café Connect – including menus and specials
- Communicate with other students through the chat function and build social communities
- News and Events – keep up to date with everything that is happening around Highlands College
- Student Services – access to dedicated support services
- See which enrichment opportunities are available to you, including Duke of Edinburgh
- View student benefits
- Careers advice
- Academic Milestones
- Admissions

Download now and start exploring!
